examples.en: He roamed about in search of work.
His eyes roamed over the bookshelves.
The cattle roamed in search of water.
They roamed the streets at a loose end.
Millions of buffalo once roamed the prairies.
We roamed around town for a while before dinner.
In the distant past, dinosaurs roamed the earth.
Spindly, underfed dogs roamed the poverty-stricken village.
